#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.135"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.135:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.135:0.2"
msgid "14. Yodhājīvavagga"
msgstr "14. A Warrior"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.135:0.3"
msgid "135. Mittasutta"
msgstr "135. A Friend"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.286"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.135:1.1"
msgid "“Tīhi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato mitto sevitabbo."
msgstr "“Mendicants, you should associate with a friend who has three factors."

#. VAR: () → (idha bhikkhave bhikkhu) (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an3.135:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi? ()"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.135:1.3"
msgid "Duddadaṃ dadāti, dukkaraṃ karoti, dukkhamaṃ khamati—"
msgstr ""
"They give what is hard to give, they do what is hard to do, and they bear "
"what is hard to bear."

msgctxt "an3.135:1.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi aṅgehi samannāgato mitto sevitabbo”ti."
msgstr "You should associate with a friend who has these three factors.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.135:1.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
